					</div>
					<div class="contact-source">
						<a href="https://www.boston.gov/departments/boston-digital-service/311-technology-modernization-project"
							target="_blank" rel="noopener">311 Modernization Project</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="contact-card">
					<div class="contact-role">City Council Oversight</div>
					<div class="contact-name">Committee on City Services &amp; Innovation Technology</div>
					<p>Chaired by Councilor Edward Flynn (D2).
						Has jurisdiction over 311, Public Works, and Inspectional Services.</p>
					<div class="contact-info">
						<a href="mailto:ccc.csit@boston.gov">ccc.csit@boston.gov</a>
					</div>
					<div class="contact-source">
						<a href="https://www.boston.gov/departments/city-council/city-services-and-innovation-technology"
							target="_blank" rel="noopener">Committee page</a>
					</div>
				</div>
